There was a four-way stop in front of her house. I could see a sign that was a street name with Hebrew writing.

00:30:42.710 --> 00:30:48.819
It was beautiful, on a green sign like we have on Earth, but not in English, with Hebrew.

00:30:48.820 --> 00:30:57.772
I didn't know what it said, but I could see it was a four-way stop, but not a stop sign, just street names.

00:30:57.773 --> 00:31:03.663
It said what street she lived on. In front of her house were beautiful flowers.

00:31:03.664 --> 00:31:14.710
She lived in a Victorian home; it looked like a plantation home, like in Mississippi or Alabama, with beautiful pillars.

00:31:14.711 --> 00:31:28.166
On the front was a huge wraparound porch with a brown rail that went all the way around where you would put your arms.

00:31:28.167 --> 00:31:32.826
Everything was beautiful white, but it was all like lattice.

00:31:32.827 --> 00:31:40.980
You know how you have those carved-out wood structures on old Victorian homes.

00:31:40.981 --> 00:31:58.529
But there were grains; you could see the grain of the wood, but there was blue on some of them, and there were beautiful colors on this shiny, lacquer-looking banister that went all the way around the porch.

00:31:58.530 --> 00:32:09.052
The gold street went all the way, and her porch went around. Her house was huge and two stories.

00:32:09.053 --> 00:32:15.947
The windows were massive picture windows across the front of her home.

00:32:15.948 --> 00:32:23.577
There were two of them and then her front door—double front doors with two wreaths.

00:32:23.578 --> 00:32:32.945
They were beautiful greenery wreaths that looked like something you would get for Easter. Beautiful colors, beautiful greens.

00:32:32.946 --> 00:32:42.702
On her front door, which had two huge columns that went up the steps to her house, I could see rocking chairs.

00:32:42.703 --> 00:32:56.528
It was the same rocking chair she used with the quilt when she was sitting there praying with Rachel for Tillar and Jeane Wilkerson, Brother Halvorsen, and the other lady—I don't know who it was.

00:32:56.529 --> 00:33:05.213
She was using that same rocking chair, but she had it on her front porch with ferns. They were beautiful ferns and things hanging down.

00:33:05.214 --> 00:33:13.899
As I was looking at her house, I tried to focus on it, but I had to focus on what she was saying.

00:33:13.900 --> 00:33:31.022
It was beautiful. The oak tree I saw her sitting by was on the corner of her house. She has massive, beautiful oak trees in her front yard.

00:33:31.023 --> 00:33:38.732
All of a sudden, she was talking to me about intercessory prayer and telling me it has to be groaned out in the spirit.

00:33:38.733 --> 00:33:50.596
Brother Kenneth Hagin walked up beside her and said, 'I have a message from the Lord to give you.'He looked young; he didn't look old.

00:33:50.597 --> 00:34:01.555
I hardly recognized him because, although his voice sounded the same, his face didn't look the same to me.

00:34:01.556 --> 00:34:16.723
He didn't look skinny like a beanpole; he still had some weight and looked thick, but he didn't look obese.

00:34:16.724 --> 00:34:29.142
As he walked up, he said to me, 'There are things I was never allowed to say on the earth that I carried, and as of tonight, you receive part of that seed.

00:34:29.143 --> 00:34:40.558
There are things I was never allowed to say, visitations from the Lord I was never allowed to tell.

00:34:40.559 --> 00:34:50.782
It's time now to birth this in the earth, to grow this forth in the earth, for it wasn't my time when I received it.

00:34:50.783 --> 00:35:03.718
But it's your turn now. Take the Word of Faith and teach the people the Word of Faith, just like I did. Teach them prayer. You have an assignment.

00:35:03.719 --> 00:35:16.332
You must finish strong.'He said there would be things I would groan out in the spirit for the impartation of things he had.

00:35:16.333 --> 00:35:26.161
'You will now receive and give this to the earth.'For it was in my time when I had it; it's your time.

00:35:26.162 --> 00:35:44.066
And he said, 'Birth it, birth it, praying it in, birth it out in prayer and travail.'And so when Brother Hagin was standing there, he said that over the last two years of the church before the Rapture, this is what you're about to see.

00:35:44.067 --> 00:35:54.748
And that's when he touched me; he imparted it. He imparted it like a Lucy, and he said, 'This is what I was not allowed to talk about.

00:35:54.749 --> 00:36:06.932
This is the last two years before the Rapture.'He said, 'This is what you're about to see: the end-time glory, and it must be birthed out.

00:36:06.933 --> 00:36:24.673
This is something I didn't talk about.'And he said, 'I saw a veil.'It looked like a veil—you know, like when you're seeing something that has a film in front of it—it looked like it was being blocked out where you couldn't see it.

00:36:24.674 --> 00:36:39.545
You couldn't make out what it was because it wasn't time. But he said over this time frame, you'll see this, and it's time now; it's time now. You are birthing this now. And I saw it, and it was a veil.

00:36:39.546 --> 00:36:51.286
As it was about the end times, he said, 'This will happen over the two years before the coming of the Lord.'And as he said all that he was supposed to say from the Lord, I felt the Holy Ghost and fire hit me.

00:36:51.287 --> 00:36:56.815
He just turned around and walked away. He didn't say anything else; he didn't say goodbye or anything, he just turned around and walked away.

00:36:56.816 --> 00:37:04.899
He walked down the same golden path, but he didn't say anything else to me. He was done, and he just turned around and walked away.

00:37:04.900 --> 00:37:13.565
He had his hands in front of him like this, and he was twiddling his fingers on his chest.

00:37:13.566 --> 00:37:20.232
And he said, 'I have a word from the Lord for you.'But he was twiddling his fingers just like this.

00:37:20.233 --> 00:37:28.583
It was kind of strange, but that's what I saw him doing; he was twiddling his fingers and he turned around and walked away.

00:37:28.584 --> 00:37:37.122
He didn't say anything else to me. As I was standing there, Jeannie Wilkerson came up.

00:37:37.123 --> 00:37:45.366
She never said anything to me; she was just grinning at me and smiled real big. Jeannie had big puffy hair, big hair.

00:37:45.367 --> 00:37:55.448
She had a bell, beautiful 1900s-like blouse on that had a ruffled collar that buttoned down, with beautiful sleeves that buttoned.

00:37:55.449 --> 00:38:06.315
They were puffy sleeves. And she just sat there and looked at me, but I could see she looked young, even though she had old people's clothes on.

00:38:06.316 --> 00:38:14.026
She had old people's clothes on, like old clothes, and she smiled at me.

00:38:14.027 --> 00:38:22.849
I was being sucked out and was coming back into my natural state out of the spirit.

00:38:22.850 --> 00:38:44.223
I said, "Oh no, wait."I could hear the angel choir singing above Lucy's house, and I could hear, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord, holy, holy, holy, holy, holy, holy."They sounded like living water; they sounded like echoes of living water.

00:38:44.224 --> 00:38:50.427
It sounded to me like a sound that never ended and never began.

00:38:50.428 --> 00:38:58.405
It was a flow. I don't know how else to describe it. It sounded like a symphony.

00:38:58.406 --> 00:39:06.924
It was the most beautiful noise; I could hear it in the atmosphere. It was gorgeous, the way they all sounded.

00:39:06.925 --> 00:39:13.902
But it wasn't just one voice; it was many voices, all singing through the atmosphere that sounded like a symphony.

00:39:13.903 --> 00:39:25.599
It was gorgeous. I could see it as I was getting pulled out. Wanting to hear more about prayer from Lucy, I stopped and asked, "Is there anything else?

00:39:25.600 --> 00:39:41.074
Is there anything else you want to say?"She said, "Tell my sister I'm more alive than I've ever been and tell her that I will see her soon.

00:39:41.075 --> 00:39:52.197
Tell her I said hi."As I was being sucked out, she turned her back to me and started walking towards her porch.

00:39:52.198 --> 00:40:05.206
I heard, "Finish strong, finish strong. You must finish strong."I was back in my heart.

00:40:05.207 --> 00:40:18.692
There are really no words; all I can tell you is heaven is so real, and it is the most beautiful thing I've ever seen in my life.

00:40:18.693 --> 00:40:31.498
Again, the Lord allowed me to see on the other side. But He said, "You're going to start to see a lot and give messages from heaven to earth.

00:40:31.499 --> 00:40:41.009
Heaven and earth are colliding and you're about to give messages from heaven to earth because there are things that need to be said."As heaven and earth collide, there are things that need to be said.

00:40:41.010 --> 00:40:53.525
There are impartations that need to happen. I saw my doorway. He said, "This is your doorway.

00:40:53.526 --> 00:41:21.466
This is your portal, and you'll start to use this a lot."I don't know what that means, if "a lot"is a lot—it's been over a year since the last one—but I'm so grateful.

00:41:21.467 --> 00:41:30.505
At the same time, I know it's a lot of responsibility. I saw all the different tribes and different stones.

00:41:30.506 --> 00:41:38.170
They were on a chart: green sapphire, red, and pinks. They looked like purple stones.

00:41:38.171 --> 00:42:04.985
And He said, "This is the 12 tribes of Israel."I saw the 12 tribes, and He showed me there would be a similarity to end-time mantles and end-time calls, different types of ministries walking in the ever-glorious outpouring that would represent different stones.

00:42:04.986 --> 00:42:12.499
They represented this, and I am still trying to figure all that out.

00:42:12.500 --> 00:42:22.676
I just thought it was something that I just couldn't keep to myself when she said, 'Tell my sister we'll see her soon.

00:42:22.677 --> 00:42:31.666
Y'all finish strong.''Tell her,'said my mom. Mom and daddy said I was blessed by it there in the great cloud of witnesses rooting for every single one of us.

00:42:31.667 --> 00:42:46.338
And I believe with all my heart Jesus is coming sooner than later, and we must birth these things out, not just by praying them in tongues, but by birth groanings that cannot be uttered.

00:42:46.339 --> 00:43:02.775
What is it that we don't know and have a revelation of to the level that we just kind of read Romans 8:26 and just kind of go, 'Okay'? That's what it was for me, and the Lord spoke through them.

00:43:02.776 --> 00:43:14.617
You must understand it's not just about praying in the spirit all the time and flowing in the rivers; this is going to come out of groanings.

00:43:14.618 --> 00:43:26.064
The greater glory will come through groanings. So I pray this video blessed you as much as it blessed me.

00:43:26.065 --> 00:43:42.009
And I pray I am a good sower. When I listen to me talking about that again, I experience it.

00:43:42.010 --> 00:43:51.299
I cherish the moments and the times I have with the Father that have changed my life forever.

00:43:51.300 --> 00:43:59.041
I can still hear the sounds; I can still see the beautiful colors.

00:43:59.042 --> 00:44:08.057
It was so intense. Lucy was a prayer warrior. She was with Lynn Hammond in Minnesota; they had Living Word.

00:44:08.058 --> 00:44:21.019
She was the pastor there. Now her son is running the church. She's a prayer warrior there; they pray on a level that most people are not familiar with.

00:44:21.020 --> 00:44:29.687
Lucy went home to be with the Lord, and she had an assignment on the other side. She told everybody.

00:44:29.688 --> 00:44:45.944
As I've talked to Sister Billie today and some of the elders about what I experienced, it's amazing because there was so much confirmed.

00:44:45.945 --> 00:44:54.525
There were things that were said that I did not make public that really validate Lucy.

00:44:54.526 --> 00:45:09.269
I never knew Lucy; I've seen her on videos before, but she was there, and I've always paid attention to her sister Lynn because she's still here on the earth.

00:45:09.270 --> 00:45:20.538
But she was a twin. It's amazing because of what the Lord said: the greater glory would be birthed, and it would be through travail.

00:45:20.539 --> 00:45:26.268
It wasn't just about praying in the spirit and praying in tongues; it's about travail in the spirit.

00:45:26.269 --> 00:45:32.601
And when she used the Scripture and she showed it to me when I was in heaven, I saw it all.

00:45:32.602 --> 00:45:39.605
And I saw Brother Hagin, Kenneth Hagin, and he was walking around. Even his mannerism—he's a very quiet man.

00:45:39.606 --> 00:45:51.908
He only spoke very little, but it was amazing because he said, "One of the things I did not say is that you're running out of time.

00:45:51.909 --> 00:46:03.390
The church is running out of time. Jesus is coming. Do you understand that?"Lucy was so adamant about letting me know that we were out of time.

00:46:03.391 --> 00:46:11.061
"You must understand that you're out of time,"she said. "I've carried this as far as I can.

00:46:11.062 --> 00:46:20.494
Now you have to do this on the earth. There must be more prayer on the earth."That's not just casual prayer.

00:46:20.495 --> 00:46:33.870
We have prayer meetings, but we don't pray. We have intercessory prayer meetings, and we hardly ever pray. The Lord said we must come up to a different level in prayer.

00:46:33.871 --> 00:46:48.655
For if we are assembling ourselves together for intercessory prayer, we must pray like we do on this channel, he said, because there are pieces of what you carry there that I don't carry.

00:46:48.656 --> 00:47:00.548
And when we all come together, we make a whole puzzle. There are giftings and abilities inside of you that God's gifted you with that he didn't give me.

00:47:00.549 --> 00:47:07.928
But that's why you may be the finger and I may be the toe, but all of us make a whole body.

00:47:07.929 --> 00:47:16.937
There's not one of us more special than another. One might be the elbow, one might be the arm, one might be the rib.

00:47:16.938 --> 00:47:27.522
Who knows? All I know is we form a whole body. Jesus is the head, but we are the body.

00:47:27.523 --> 00:47:32.875
Jesus turns the body, and we are his if we allow him to be in control.

00:47:32.876 --> 00:47:40.726
But we always like—as I've told you a thousand times—we always stay vertical and we keep humble.

00:47:40.727 --> 00:47:46.079
None of us can do any of this without his grace and by his mercy.

00:47:46.080 --> 00:47:57.257
I don't care how much you think you have a gift; it's all by his grace that you have it in the first place. And it's time the church woke up.

00:47:57.258 --> 00:48:05.366
And the Lord showed me, even when Brother Hagin—I'm telling you, it was the way he talked was very stern.

00:48:05.367 --> 00:48:15.338
But he was walking in love. But there was such a seriousness in what they both had to say to me.

00:48:15.339 --> 00:48:25.238
It wasn't like we just brought you up here to talk to you because we like you.

00:48:25.239 --> 00:48:33.555
No, this was like battle cries: "We're telling you what's coming. You need to wake up. You must warn the church.

00:48:33.556 --> 00:48:47.228
You must tell the church."And then Brother Hagin said there were private things that he told me that I will not say on this platform.

00:48:47.229 --> 00:49:02.805
It was about me and my ministry. But there are certain things that even I have got to grow in as he prayed for me.

00:49:02.806 --> 00:49:25.862
You know, when you have somebody that you look up to a lot and you've listened to him as a little boy—a young man—all through my teenage years, listening to teaching after teaching, and then have a face-to-face meeting with him in heaven after he's gone and be able to see him talk to me.

00:49:25.863 --> 00:49:45.573
And he knew my name. I went, 'Oh.'I don't give man any praise, but there are certain people that have helped me along the way and helped me stay.

00:49:45.574 --> 00:49:58.291
Whenever Megan was first diagnosed with autism and his teachings helped us—Diana and I both—I'm so thankful that God would allow me to talk to him.

00:49:58.292 --> 00:50:10.638
And an impartation happened—that and the fire that hit me—and for prayer and for the things that he told me I was going to do.

00:50:10.639 --> 00:50:23.266
I don't know what the Lord meant by a portal to bring messages back and to say things; I don't know what all that means. I'm still praying over it.

00:50:23.267 --> 00:50:43.728
But Brother Hagin said, right before the coming of the Lord, 'For what I have seen, the impartation of what I was never able to reveal was that the revival will take place for two years.'And whenever he gave it over, it looked like a kumquat, one of those little fruits.

00:50:43.729 --> 00:50:59.038
And he had it, and it dropped inside of me. And he said to me, 'Impart a part of...'what I thought was interesting about the revival and what he said about the two years and things that he said.

00:50:59.039 --> 00:51:15.506
When I talked to Sister Billie on the phone today, we talked for over an hour about all this and went over the things that the Lord had shown me because she judges all the words, and if she feels something is off, she always will correct me.

00:51:15.507 --> 00:51:21.438
But as I delivered this, she said, 'I believe that's right.'She was real sweet about it.

00:51:21.439 --> 00:51:28.686
She listened because she knew these people personally. And she told me a story about another man of God.

00:51:28.687 --> 00:51:37.910
I don't know if I have her permission to talk about it, so I won't, but she talked about some other elders and things that have happened similarly.

00:51:37.911 --> 00:51:47.267
So that's what I'll say. But it just gets me excited for where we are, ladies and gentlemen, and how Jesus is coming so soon.

00:51:47.268 --> 00:51:54.506
I want you to be ready; I want you to have an anticipation for what's about to happen.

00:51:54.507 --> 00:52:06.089
When I saw the emerald color of this new fire, what I was trying to describe was what the Lord was showing me about the 12 tribes of Israel.

00:52:06.090 --> 00:52:10.071
Every single one had a stone, and an emerald represented something.

00:52:10.072 --> 00:52:19.390
And he said, 'Sapphires Healing Ministry.'And he went on and he told me what each color represented. And the red was prophetic; emerald was watchmen.

00:52:19.391 --> 00:52:25.484
There were certain things that were attached to intercessory prayer gifts and what they were attached to.

00:52:25.485 --> 00:52:30.144
The stones—a color represented something: the twelve tribes, the tribes of Israel.

00:52:30.145 --> 00:52:42.151
But he said, 'I have these mantles for the end times with key generals that will walk in the days ahead.'And Jesus spoke to me: 'That's the fire.'And it was a ball of fire.

00:52:42.152 --> 00:52:48.662
And he spoke to me—and I didn't get into all what he said—but it was the most beautiful, green, beautiful experience.

00:52:48.663 --> 00:52:52.342
As he said, 'This door was opening,'and he said, 'I want you.

00:52:52.343 --> 00:53:05.691
You're going to start to travel in between, and heaven and earth will collide.'Now, as of the first of Passover, there'll be an acceleration of things.

00:53:05.692 --> 00:53:16.733
He warned me again: it's time for breakthrough; it's time for an acceleration of things.

00:53:16.734 --> 00:53:24.463
On Passover, which is Wednesday, you will see a doubling of the birthing pains.

00:53:24.464 --> 00:53:35.571
And so we talked about this, and I probably say that the Shemitah cycle goes into 2028 to 2029.

00:53:35.572 --> 00:53:50.450
And I was talking about how we both—and even what she—we talked about it so many times about how the Shemitah cycle—the rapture of the church—will start during the Shemitah cycle of that period of 2028-2029.

00:53:50.451 --> 00:53:55.987
Not that it could be this seven-year cycle, but it could be the next seven-year cycle.

00:53:55.988 --> 00:54:02.469
But it will always be at the end of a seven-year Shemitah cycle.

00:54:02.470 --> 00:54:15.216
And so she was talking about how it's up, and when Brother Hagin said, 'Two years,'could it be 2027-2028 for the great outpouring of what he was talking about?

00:54:15.217 --> 00:54:26.505
And going over things, I just want you to have an expectation that something major is about to happen in this earth, as we see Israel and the escalation of war.

00:54:26.506 --> 00:54:34.760
And the Lord says, 'I am bringing liberation to the people.'And a major revival is coming, and great pressure is coming on Canada.

00:54:34.761 --> 00:54:39.231
And you see them pass the bills like the Lord said they would.

00:54:39.232 --> 00:54:49.338
Everything is lining up for a major persecution, for a major beast system coming, for a shaking of finances with the oil—a shaking of finances with these things.

00:54:49.339 --> 00:54:57.301
And we could be right on the edge of a major move of God. Are you ready for it tonight?

00:54:57.302 --> 00:55:04.884
Before we go on to the prayer part of this, I have to keep asking you: is your church ready?

00:55:04.885 --> 00:55:12.088
Are you ready? Are you looking for the signs of the times? Are you looking at them?

00:55:12.089 --> 00:55:21.965
Are you seeing them? Do you have your eyes to the skies? Is your heart full with oil for him?

00:55:21.966 --> 00:55:30.325
Are you looking for him? Are you yearning for him? Jesus, I can't do this life without you.

00:55:30.326 --> 00:55:42.271
I just want to encourage you tonight to be all in. It's time to come up higher in our prayer time.

00:55:42.272 --> 00:55:52.716
We will not get the job done until it's birthed in the spirit first, and it will come through travail. It will come through prayer.

00:55:52.717 --> 00:56:04.981
So ask the Holy Spirit tonight to give you a greater gift of intercessory prayer to pray for the nations, to stir up the gift that you already have.

00:56:04.982 --> 00:56:14.342
But to go deeper with him is what I'm trying to say. Not just ankle-deep, not just knee-deep, not just waist-deep.

00:56:14.343 --> 00:56:22.518
Let's go to the bottom of the pool. We must come up higher, and you must surrender more to him.

00:56:22.519 --> 00:56:35.727
Jesus, I want to help you. Use me. Teach me to pray on another level. I want to be one of your end-time prayer warriors.

00:56:35.728 --> 00:56:47.288
The Lord told us you'll bring prayer to the nations, and in doing so, there will be a million-man and woman prayer army eventually with you.

00:56:47.289 --> 00:56:57.235
You will pray, and you will change things, and it will bring forth the glorious outpouring as we pray together.

00:56:57.236 --> 00:57:02.973
He said, 'Brandon, I've assembled the greatest prayer warriors of this generation on this channel.

00:57:02.974 --> 00:57:12.638
They're coming. I'm commissioning them. I'm stirring them up to come.'So tonight I have to ask you: Are you all in?

00:57:12.639 --> 00:57:19.309
Are you looking for him? Is your heart hungry for the King? How desperate, how thirsty?

00:57:19.310 --> 00:57:28.481
How bad is your want-to to go into the deeper rivers? He's a gentleman. He'll never force his way on you.

00:57:28.482 --> 00:57:35.578
He'll always be the polite one knocking on the door, saying, 'Will you let me in?

00:57:35.579 --> 00:57:46.136
Will you let me in? I'm knocking on the door of your heart. Will you let me in?'It's your job to say, 'Here, my Lord.

00:57:46.137 --> 00:57:52.497
Send me.'Like Esther, I've been called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:57:52.498 --> 00:58:03.627
As we go into this Holy Week—Passover, Good Friday, Resurrection Sunday—what will the people get when they come to your church?

00:58:03.628 --> 00:58:17.938
We must pray over the protection of our pastors, our churches, and our synagogues—wherever you're going, wherever you're at—for the Jews, for every one of them, for a great protection around and about us.

00:58:17.939 --> 00:58:25.738
Because the Lord showed me major planned attacks like what happened on Palm Sunday in Nigeria.

00:58:25.739 --> 00:58:36.498
All those people are dead now. I want to ask you tonight: Do you know my friend Jesus? Do you know him?

00:58:36.499 --> 00:58:46.534
And if you're here tonight and you say, 'Brannon, all that sounds so wonderful, but I don't even know Jesus.'I don't even know where I would go if I die.

00:58:46.535 --> 00:58:58.086
I want to lead you in a simple little prayer. But I want you to be bold before we move on and just tell everybody in the comment section, 'I want to be saved tonight.

00:58:58.087 --> 00:59:05.477
I want to accept Jesus Christ. I want to accept him before it's too late.'Brother Hagin, they say you're running out of time.

00:59:05.478 --> 00:59:10.471
And even if it was two years, even if it's just a year, I don't know.

00:59:10.472 --> 00:59:20.573
If we're in that time frame right now, in the next two years, whatever, I truly believe that we truly are running out of time on this dispensation of grace.

00:59:20.574 --> 00:59:24.613
But you're here tonight and you feel that tugging on your heart.

00:59:24.614 --> 00:59:30.338
